weakness":[]}]},"part2":{"weakness_suggest":["Physical","Imaginary"],"totalWaves":2,"wave1":[{"monster_name":"Dreamjolt Troupe's Sweet Gorilla","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Imaginary"]},{"monster_name":"Aurumaton Spectral Envoy","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Thunder","Imaginary"]}],"wave2":[{"monster_name":"Ichor Memosprite: Judge of Oblivion","monster_code":4,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Ice","Imaginary"]}]}},{"name":{"zh_cn":"堤溃蚁穴其十二","zh_hk":"堤潰蟻穴其十二","de":"Zerstörtes Nest XII","en":"Breached Nest (XII)","es":"Nido quebrado XII","fr":"Brèche dans la digue (XII)","id":"Kehancuran oleh Lubang Semut <unbreak>12</unbreak>","jp":"蟻の一穴・<unbreak>12</unbreak>","kr":"제방을 허무는 개미굴•<unbreak>12</unbreak>","pt":"Covil Aterrador (XII)","ru":"Разрушенное гнездо XII","th":"รังมดพังเขื่อน <unbreak>12</unbreak>","vi":"Đê Sập Vì Hang Kiến <unbreak>12</unbreak>"},"part1":{"weakness_suggest":["Fire","Quantum"],"totalWaves":2,"wave1":[{"monster_name":"Dark Sun Gryphon","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Quantum"]},{"monster_name":"Ice Out of Space","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Fire","Wind","Quantum"]}],"wave2":[{"monster_name":"Cocolia","monster_code":0,"monster_weakness":["Fire","Thunder","Quantum"]},{"monster_name":"Bronya","monster_code":-1,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Imaginary"]}]},"part2":{"weakness_suggest":["Physical","Fire"],"totalWaves":2,"wave1":[{"monster_name":"Lady of Crashing Waves","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Thunder"]},{"monster_name":"Ichor Memosprite: Winged Serpent","monster_code":3,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Ice"]}],"wave2":[{"monster_name":"Harbinger of Death: Swarm Nightmare","monster_code":4,"monster_weakness":["Physical","Fire","Wind"]}]}}],"name":{"zh_cn":"堤溃蚁穴","zh_hk":"堤潰蟻穴","de":"Zerstörtes Nest","en":"Breached Nest","es":"Nido quebrado","fr":"Brèche dans la digue","id":"Kehancuran oleh Lubang Semut","jp":"蟻の一穴","kr":"제방을 허무는 개미굴","pt":"Covil Aterrador","ru":"Разрушенное гнездо","th":"รังมดพังเขื่อน","vi":"Đê Sập Vì Hang Kiến"},"desc":{"zh_cn":"每个波次开始时，为我方恢复4个战技点，我方目标施放战技或消耗战技点时，为【记忆紊流】增加1段攻击段数，最多叠加15段。\\n每个轮开始时，【记忆紊流】的每段攻击对随机敌方目标造成1次真实伤害。","zh_hk":"每一波開始時，為我方恢復4個戰技點，我方目標施放戰技或消耗戰技點時，為【記憶紊流】增加1段攻擊段數，最多疊加15段。\\n每一輪開始時，【記憶紊流】的每段攻擊對隨機敵方目標造成1次真實傷害。","de":"Stellt zu Beginn jeder Kampfwelle 4 Fertigkeitspunkte für Verbündete wieder her. Wenn Verbündete eine Fertigkeit einsetzen oder Fertigkeitspunkte verbrauchen, wird die Trefferzahl von „Turbulenzen des Gedächtnisses“ um 1 erhöht, bis zu 15.\\nZu Beginn jeder Runde fügt jeder Treffer von „Turbulenzen des Gedächtnisses“ einem zufälligen Gegner 1-mal Tatsächlichen SCH zu.","en":"At the start of each wave, recovers 4 Skill Point(s) for allies. When ally targets use Skills or consume Skill Points, add 1 hits to \"Memory Turbulence,\" stacking up to 15 hit(s).\\nAt the start of each Cycle, each hit of \"Memory Turbulence\" deals True DMG once to a random enemy target.","es":"Al comenzar cada oleada, los aliados recuperan 4 pts. de habilidad básica. Cuando un aliado lanza una habilidad básica o consume pts. de habilidad básica, añade 1 golpe por acción a Recuerdo turbulento, hasta un máximo de 15 golpes.\\nAl comenzar cada ciclo, cada golpe de Recuerdo turbulento inflige Daño verdadero una vez a un enemigo al azar.","fr":"Au début de chaque vague, les alliés récupèrent 4 points de compétence. Lorsqu'une cible alliée utilise une compétence ou consomme des points de compétence, ajoute 1 frappe à la Turbulence mémorielle, jusqu'à un maximum de 15 frappes.\\nAu début de chaque cycle, chaque frappe infligée par la Turbulence mémorielle inflige une instance de DGT réels à une cible ennemie aléatoire.","id":"Saat setiap gelombang pertempuran dimulai, memulihkan 4 Poin Skill rekan tim. Saat rekan tim melancarkan Skill atau mengonsumsi Poin Skill, akan menambah 1 Hits Per Action bagi \"Memory Turbulence\", dapat ditumpuk hingga 15 Hit.\\nSaat setiap putaran dimulai, setiap Hit \"Memory Turbulence\" akan mengakibatkan 1 kali True DMG pada target musuh acak.","jp":"各ウェーブ開始時、味方のSPを4回復する。味方が戦闘スキルを発動、またはSPを消費した時、「記憶の乱流」の攻撃段数が1段アップする。最大で15段累積できる。\\n各ラウンド開始時、1段の攻撃につきランダムな敵に確定ダメージを1回与える。","kr":"웨이브가 시작될 때마다 아군의 전투 스킬 포인트를 4pt 회복한다. 아군이 전투 스킬 발동 또는 전투 스킬 포인트 소모 시, [기억의 와류]의 공격 단수가 1단 증가하며, 최대 15단 중첩된다.\\n라운드가 시작될 때마다 [기억의 와류]의 공격 단수마다 랜덤 적에게 확정 피해를 1회 가한다","pt":"No início de cada onda, recupera 4 Ponto(s) de Perícia para os aliados. Quando os aliados-alvo usam Perícias ou consomem Pontos de Perícia, adiciona 1 golpe(s) à \"Turbulência de Memória\", acumulando até 15 golpe(s).\\nNo início de cada Ciclo, cada golpe de \"Turbulência de Memória\" causa <u>Dano Verdadeiro</u> uma vez a um inimigo-alvo aleatório.","ru":"В начале каждой волны восстанавливается 4 оч. навыков отряда. Когда союзник использует навык или расходует очки навыков, он добавляет Турбулентности памяти 1 удар до макс. 15 ударов.\\nВ начале каждого цикла каждый удар Турбулентности памяти наносит случайному противнику истинный урон 1 раз.","th":"เมื่อเริ่มต้นในแต่ละ Wave จะฟื้นฟูแต้มสกิลต่อสู้ให้แก่ฝ่ายเรา 4 แต้ม เมื่อเป้าหมายฝ่ายเราปล่อยสกิลต่อสู้ หรือใช้แต้มสกิลต่อสู้ จะเพิ่มจำนวนการโจมตีให้กับ \"Memory Turbulence\" 1 ครั้ง และสามารถซ้อนทับได้สูงสุด 15 ครั้ง\\nเมื่อเริ่มต้นในแต่ละรอบ การโจมตีแต่ละครั้งของ \"Memory Turbulence\" จะสร้าง DMG จริง ให้แก่ศัตรูแบบสุ่มเป้าหมาย 1 ครั้ง","vi":"Khi bắt đầu mỗi đợt, hồi phục 4 Điểm Chiến Kỹ cho phe ta, khi mục tiêu phe ta thi triển Chiến Kỹ hoặc tiêu hao Điểm Chiến Kỹ, sẽ tăng thêm 1 đòn đánh trong một lượt cho \"Dòng Hồi Ức Rối Loạn\", tối đa cộng dồn 15 đòn.\\nVào đầu mỗi vòng, mỗi đòn tấn công của \"Dòng Hồi Ức Rối Loạn\" gây 1 lần Sát Thương Chuẩn lên mục tiêu phe địch ngẫu nhiên."},"time":{"begin":1768766400000,"end":1772395200000,"versionBegin":"3.8","versionEnd":"3.8"}}